namespace pdg { /**

\fn pdg::Sprite::onOnscreen

\brief set event handler for sprite onscreen event

This happens whenever this sprite moves into the visible area of the port the layer is being rendered into, but only if you first call setWantsOffscreenEvents(true)

\sa setWantsOffscreenEvents()
\sa onOffscreen()
\sa SpriteAnimateEvent
\sa IEventHandler


**/ }